descriptionHtml:
*Are you a Pro Wrestling fanatic? Test your knowledge & take the challenge!
*Entertaining and Fun game! Reach the Belt first!
*Access achievements which give you bonus hints!
*Take the Challenge and test your skills! It's free to play!
*Questions are in random order and do not repeat!

The clock is ticking, so be quick and make the correct selection to earn extra bonus points. The quicker you select correctly, the more bonus points you earn. You can still take as long as you like to select an answer but no bonus points are given.

Get 50 correct questions and reach the Champions Belt!

*Use your Google Play login to check your ranking on the leader boards. Compare with players around the world. You can see your best high individual score and also your total cumulative score. Challenge friends and see who can reach the top of the leader boards.

Compete now and download for Free now!
